data.description: ASSUMABLE FHA LOAN at 3.5%!!!! Beautiful single level home that offers 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and an open concept floorplan with large living room area. Enjoy desert living in your professionally designed and landscaped backyard. The home sits on a lot that backs the wash giving you unobstructed views of the desert and ultimate privacy, with no neighbors behind you!  The community of Anthem at Merrill Ranch offers a lap pool, water slide, splash pad, along with recreational areas, a gym, tennis courts, indoor basketball and more!
